# This .gitignore file is expanded to the directory where `ign checkout` is executed.
# It is NOT for the ign-template repository itself.

# Python environments and caches
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/__pycache__/
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/
**/.coverage
**/.coverage.*
**/*.py[cod]
**/*.egg-info/
**/.python-version

# Build artifacts
/build/
/dist/
**/*.whl
**/*.tar.gz
htmlcov/

## nix/git
/.pre-commit-config.yaml
**/.direnv
**/.env
**/.envrc.private*
**/*.private*

## ide's /meta infos
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/.~lock*
**/.DS_Store

## tmp and local outputs
result
**/tmp
